column2: SELECT t.thingid, t.ndetect, d.objid, r.Sdssdr9SourceId_#, p.dec, r.GaiaDEC_#, p.ra, r.GaiaRA_# into mydb.AllThingIds FROM thingIndex AS t JOIN detectionindex AS d ON t.thingid = d.thingid JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON d.objid = p.objid JOIN mydb.FinalRawData AS r ON p.objid = r.Sdssdr9SourceId_# order by t.ndetect
